      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. While the exterior paint still looks great, you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with normal driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and a few faint marks on the floor mats. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
