    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride with plenty of character? This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready to take you on your next adventure! It has served its previous owners well and, while it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid and functional choice. With a little bit of care, this car has many more miles to give\u2014perfect for someone seeking value and dependability!",
